        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Urban farmers and hobbyist gardeners in Malaysia are discovering indoor hydroponics and vertical gardening as solutions to limited outdoor space. Building sturdy, affordable shelving systems for grow lights, water systems, and plant containers requires affordable, strong materials. Corrugated cardboard sheets from Quinocycle provide an ideal, budget-friendly foundation for DIY hydroponics projects.</p>
