        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Line cardboard shelves with waterproof plastic sheeting, sealed fabric membranes, or specialized coatings. This protects corrugated sheets from water splash and humidity while maintaining structural integrity through Malaysia's rainy seasons.</p>

