        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Stack corrugated sheets 4–5 levels high with support brackets. Each tier holds grow trays, seedlings, or potted plants. Space each shelf 40–50cm apart for adequate grow light coverage in hydroponic systems.</p>

