        <p class="font-body text-on-surface leading-relaxed mb-6">Attach small pockets or pouches to vertical corrugated sheets to create living walls. Perfect for herbs, leafy greens, and small vegetables in urban gardening setups across Balakong, Klang Valley, and metropolitan areas.</p>
